    bullets: [
      'Website rebuilt for PATH commuters, locals, and corporate tenants with mobile-first design and bilingual sections.',
      'Google Business Profile optimized with waterfront photography, neighborhood-specific keywords, and commuter-friendly hours.',
      'Review engine deployed with QR codes and automated requests targeting Jersey City neighborhoods.',
