      'Retention flows segmented by neighborhood and commuter vs. resident audiences—all human-monitored.',
    ],
    accent: 'yellow',
  },
  {
    title: 'Neighborhood Domination ($3,750/mo)',
    bullets: [
      'Everything in Growth Engine, plus guaranteed weekly HudPost coverage and local influencer coordination.',
      'Ad Engine targeting Jersey City commuters, Downtown professionals, and neighborhood residents searching with intent.',
      'VIP event management, seasonal campaigns, and priority capture scheduling across all Jersey City neighborhoods.',
    ],
    accent: 'pink',
  },
